14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 255.10 of Title 62, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 A. The Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall
19 develop a form for use by each agency, board, commission, department
20 or other entity organized within the executive branch of state
21 government for use by such governmental entity in identifying
22 prospective vendors for contracts to manage federal funds if such
23 funds management is permissible pursuant to the federal law enabling
24 and transferring such funds for expenditure by the state
